<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>404 - Page non trouvée</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f8ff;
      color: #333;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .icon {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin: 0 0 20px;
    }
    a.button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #007acc;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    a.button:hover {
      background-color: #005fa3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="#007acc" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="32" opacity="0.2"/>
    <text x="32" y="37" font-size="28" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial" fill="#007acc">?</text>
  </svg>

  <h1>404</h1>
  <p>Désolé, la page que vous recherchez est introuvable.</p>
  <a href="/" class="button">Retour à l'accueil</a>
</body>
</html>
